{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/free-movement-people/gatherings","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Gatherings","meta_description":"Rules for organizing demonstrations, restrictions on the number of people and hygiene measures.","content":{"processed":"<p><strong>Rules and Recommendations</strong></p>\n<p>The government's measures restricted the right to peaceful assembly. If you want to go or organize a demonstration, there must <strong>not be more than 100 </strong>of you, you must be<strong> in groups </strong>of a <strong>maximum of 20 participants </strong>and you must keep the <strong>spacing</strong> between groups <strong>at least 2 meters</strong>. All participants at the demonstration must wear a face mask or other respiratory protection. Demonstrations must also take place outdoors (i.e. not indoors, such as halls, cultural centers, etc.).</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people/gatherings"},"changed":"2020-11-18T18:55:01+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-04T23:45:51+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://www.vlada.cz/assets/media-centrum/aktualne/uv201116-1190.pdf","title":"Government measures on the free movement of persons"}],"relationships":{"region":[],"icon":{"code":"directions_walk"},"situation_type":{"name":"Free movement of people","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"directions_walk"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[]},"questions_answers":[],"valid_to":"2020-11-20T23:59:59+01:00","last_updated":"2020-11-09T09:36:02+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Free movement of people","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"directions_walk"},"situation":[{"id":"7ae65304-9098-5acd-a19f-973af8c793b7","title":"Measures on free movement","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people/measures-free-movement"}},{"id":"69089399-f5ce-52e0-ab8